<p begin="24020000t" end="38920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40040000t" end="73030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74070000t" end="142100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260260000t" end="303600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="304640000t" end="374270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="414750000t" end="496100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="516510000t" end="531750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="532860000t" end="565510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566560000t" end="618210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619280000t" end="668880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670000000t" end="732000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="801470000t" end="830820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;第17話 執行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="866860000t" end="910890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;就像這樣繼續殺掉&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;被報導出來的罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="911910000t" end="942510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;你就可以隨意使用&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這本筆記本了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="943610000t" end="959190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;這就是交換條件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="968970000t" end="1013910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;如果夜神月猜想的沒錯&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這樣應該可以讓海砂得救&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1026360000t" end="1073000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;對我們雙方來說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都是一筆好交易吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1074070000t" end="1114000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;以你的說法&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「這是一筆好生意」吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1169500000t" end="1178140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;(囚禁第50天)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1179180000t" end="1195100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;夜神局長,你沒事吧?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1204870000t" end="1233200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;其實你不用這樣為難自己的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1239570000t" end="1294520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;KIRA再次制裁罪犯至今&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;已經超過一個月了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1295630000t" end="1332600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;我確信我兒子不是KIRA了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1333660000t" end="1375980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;接下來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就看你什麼時候會相信了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1377040000t" end="1413330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;我要和兒子一起走出這裡的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1433100000t" end="1450390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;局長也很固執呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1466460000t" end="1484090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;月,你沒事吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1500500000t" end="1511420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;我還好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1518520000t" end="1568460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;龍崎,自從我被囚禁&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就再也沒有罪犯死亡了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1569570000t" end="1620880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;從這一點看來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;KIRA知道我現況的可能性很高&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1621950000t" end="1668250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;可以沿著這條線索…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不,那是因為月就是KIRA的關係&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1669330000t" end="1705280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;不是,我不是KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;要我說多少次你才明白&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1717710000t" end="1760030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;他是的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;一定會知道KIRA又開始殺人的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1761090000t" end="1774740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;但看起來不像&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1783450000t" end="1801080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;龍崎太過分了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1802130000t" end="1841490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;他居然還沒告訴月&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;罪犯被殺的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1858190000t" end="1869450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;彌海砂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1870530000t" end="1881790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1882880000t" end="1901530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;你好像沒什麼精神耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1908910000t" end="1928250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;你是笨蛋嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1929260000t" end="1962250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;過了幾十天還很有精神的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那才奇怪吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1971300000t" end="1985970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;你說的有道理&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1993320000t" end="2013230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;快點放了我吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2014340000t" end="2035270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;我想見月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2036370000t" end="2083360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;月,月…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2099430000t" end="2129350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;他們3人似乎都到極限了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2130460000t" end="2161060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;龍崎,為什麼還繼續囚禁月?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2162160000t" end="2198790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;該放他了吧,這樣局長也能出來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2199860000t" end="2245480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;彌和月都無法得到情報&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而罪犯卻還是持續被殺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2246580000t" end="2274910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;這樣就足夠證明他們的清白吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2275940000t" end="2332260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;不,我只感受到了彌對夜神月&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那種超乎尋常的愛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2342000000t" end="2364640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;龍崎,不好意思…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2365700000t" end="2425660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;我想你是不願承認&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;自己的推理錯誤才會這麼堅持的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2426760000t" end="2442340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;你果然是這麼想的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2454120000t" end="2499740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;就像月說的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;KIRA殺了冒牌的L和FBI的探員&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2500830000t" end="2525170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;照現在的情況,他也能殺人的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2526190000t" end="2553150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;就沒必要殺了那些人了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2554220000t" end="2585500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;再怎麼調查也找不到線索的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2586580000t" end="2631520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;你也說過KIRA不會盲目的殺人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2638630000t" end="2670260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;原來如此&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這種情況下也能殺人的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2671330000t" end="2705000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;就算不理FBI探員&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也不會妨礙到KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2725390000t" end="2744390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;已經50天了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2745410000t" end="2769410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;這樣下去也沒有意義&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2770430000t" end="2803420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;應該想想&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;該如何抓到真正的KIRA吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2972300000t" end="2984580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3010670000t" end="3023640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;夜神局長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3024690000t" end="3036630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;什麼事?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3037700000t" end="3066710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;能不能請你回總部來一下呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3067730000t" end="3099700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;想請你聽聽我對這件事的結論&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3108440000t" end="3144050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;以月的父親身份來聽&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3159490000t" end="3170410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3401730000t" end="3437340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;沒想到偷窺狂&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;竟然是這麼老的大叔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3438430000t" end="3469030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;我不是偷窺狂,是刑警&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3470130000t" end="3479450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;刑警?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3490150000t" end="3501410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;我想起來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3502500000t" end="3548460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;之前說我是第二KIRA嫌犯的事&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是當真的嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3561890000t" end="3611830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;不會吧,警方哪會用&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那麼瘋狂的方法抓人呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3612940000t" end="3662880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;既然要放我走卻還銬住手腳&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;很奇怪耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3663990000t" end="3675590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;請閉嘴&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3802460000t" end="3818730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;月&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;海砂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3819810000t" end="3837440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;月,我好想你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3838500000t" end="3859430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;爸爸,這是怎麼回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3860520000t" end="3870190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;爸爸?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3871200000t" end="3910220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;討厭&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我竟然這麼失禮說他是偷窺狂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3911240000t" end="3939910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;幸會,我是彌海砂&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我正在和月交往&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3940940000t" end="3955610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;拜託了,局長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3989320000t" end="4007970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle86">&#x202a;怎麼,快點上車&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4067730000t" end="4105390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle87">&#x202a;終於洗清嫌疑了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;算是恢復自由了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4111770000t" end="4163760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle88">&#x202a;不,接下來要帶你們去死刑場&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4179840000t" end="4243550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle89">&#x202a;我的任務就是護送你們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;去某建築物底下,極機密的刑場&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4244570000t" end="4256850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle90">&#x202a;死刑場?&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4257920000t" end="4275550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle91">&#x202a;爸爸,你在說什麼&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;別開玩笑了,父親大人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4276600000t" end="4324950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle92">&#x202a;L斷定夜神月是KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;彌海砂是第二KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4325990000t" end="4376620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle93">&#x202a;他說只要殺了你們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就不會再有KIRA殺人事件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4377710000t" end="4401030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle94">&#x202a;不是已經停了嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4402060000t" end="4419350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle95">&#x202a;不,還持續著&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4420410000t" end="4461710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle96">&#x202a;持續著?他不是這樣跟我說的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4462790000t" end="4500100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle97">&#x202a;那只是L為了讓你坦白&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而採取的手段&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4501160000t" end="4519130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle98">&#x202a;那不是重點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4526850000t" end="4582480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle99">&#x202a;聯合國,政府&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;及所有高層也都同意了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4583580000t" end="4625560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle100">&#x202a;L說只要殺了你們倆…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就能解決KIRA殺人的事件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4626620000t" end="4663590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle101">&#x202a;KIRA將會神不知鬼不覺的被制裁&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4664660000t" end="4694350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle102">&#x202a;別胡說了,爸爸&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我不是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4695360000t" end="4718340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle103">&#x202a;是啊,父親大人,你在想什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4719380000t" end="4734280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle104">&#x202a;他是你的兒子耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4735400000t" end="4772710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle105">&#x202a;這不是我決定的,是L決定的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4780770000t" end="4828780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle106">&#x202a;過去解決多起困難的案件&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;他從來沒有出錯過&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4839170000t" end="4875460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle107">&#x202a;爸爸,你比較相信L嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4882210000t" end="4941820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle108">&#x202a;如果這樣還是不能解決&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;L說他將會以死謝罪&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4956280000t" end="4982220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle109">&#x202a;L到底在想什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4983310000t" end="5029270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle110">&#x202a;的確,從之前的線索&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也難怪他會這麼推論&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5030360000t" end="5072680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle111">&#x202a;但這是錯的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;L怎麼會作出這種結論?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5082410000t" end="5120070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle112">&#x202a;有點奇怪,一點都不像L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5121110000t" end="5162750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle113">&#x202a;他之前分析事件時&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都會舉出確切的證據&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5163820000t" end="5181790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle114">&#x202a;這次他想草草了事?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5188520000t" end="5203420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle115">&#x202a;好了,到了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5382710000t" end="5398980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle116">&#x202a;這是哪裡?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5400060000t" end="5431340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle117">&#x202a;帶我們到這種沒有人的地方&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;要做什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5438100000t" end="5462100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle118">&#x202a;父親大人難道是想放我們走?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5468460000t" end="5504410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle119">&#x202a;是啊,這樣就不會有人看見了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5505500000t" end="5546110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle120">&#x202a;我擅自把你們帶到這裡&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而不是去刑場&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5563890000t" end="5572870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle121">&#x202a;月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5592250000t" end="5619890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle122">&#x202a;我會在這裡殺了你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;然後再自殺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5628290000t" end="5642620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle123">&#x202a;爸爸,你在說什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5643640000t" end="5666960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle124">&#x202a;別說了,爸爸你好奇怪&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;別這樣啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5667990000t" end="5710650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle125">&#x202a;殺了自己的孩子再自殺?&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;想死就自己去死不就好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5711700000t" end="5733310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle126">&#x202a;你這樣跟KIRA有什麼不同&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5734390000t" end="5752020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle127">&#x202a;不,我和KIRA不同&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5753080000t" end="5800750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle128">&#x202a;這是我身為父親&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;身為局長的責任&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5801790000t" end="5821130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle129">&#x202a;爸爸,海砂說的對&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5822150000t" end="5850130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle130">&#x202a;死在這裡的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就永遠不會知道真相了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5851180000t" end="5877800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle131">&#x202a;還是逃走吧&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;已經太遲了,月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5887210000t" end="5910530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle132">&#x202a;無論如何你都會被槍決&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5911570000t" end="5935230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle133">&#x202a;那至少讓我親手…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5960620000t" end="5984280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle134">&#x202a;住手,爸爸&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我不是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5985310000t" end="6003960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle135">&#x202a;我死了就中了KIRA的圈套了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6005000000t" end="6015580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle136">&#x202a;你不明白嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6031020000t" end="6094390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle137">&#x202a;彌,我和兒子要死在這裡&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但我沒有理由動手殺你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6095420000t" end="6127050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle138">&#x202a;警方很快就會追來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6128120000t" end="6159400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle139">&#x202a;你就到真正的刑場去受死吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6193850000t" end="6203740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle140">&#x202a;月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6216880000t" end="6245890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle141">&#x202a;殺人犯的我們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;地獄裡再見吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6257580000t" end="6266220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle142">&#x202a;爸爸&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6299630000t" end="6319310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle143">&#x202a;住手啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6343340000t" end="6367000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle144">&#x202a;(死神之眼的能力)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(會因筆記本所有權的喪失而消失)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6368030000t" end="6393630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle145">&#x202a;(但被減半的壽命卻無法回復)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6394720000t" end="6419400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle146">&#x202a;(死亡筆記本的持有人)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(可將筆記本借給他人使用)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6420410000t" end="6441680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle147">&#x202a;(而借用的人也可以再將其借出)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6457780000t" end="6472450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle148">&#x202a;月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6473470000t" end="6496790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle149">&#x202a;殺人犯的我們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;地獄裡再見吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6497820000t" end="6506460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle150">&#x202a;爸爸&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6709370000t" end="6719610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle151">&#x202a;空包彈?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6761090000t" end="6780430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle152">&#x202a;太好了…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6781440000t" end="6819440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle153">&#x202a;太好了?&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;爸爸你是什麼意思?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6820480000t" end="6841410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle154">&#x202a;你們原諒我吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6842500000t" end="6886530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle155">&#x202a;為了能釋放你們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我不得不這麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6887550000t" end="6905520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle156">&#x202a;不過請諒解&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6906560000t" end="6943190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle157">&#x202a;我是堅信你們不是KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;才這麼做的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6951940000t" end="6968890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle158">&#x202a;龍崎,你看到了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6969960000t" end="7006590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle159">&#x202a;我照你說的做了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但是還是活得好好的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7020350000t" end="7044690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle160">&#x202a;是的,很逼真的演技&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7052710000t" end="7097080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle161">&#x202a;如果彌是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;看到相貌就能殺人的第二KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7098090000t" end="7143370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle162">&#x202a;在月被槍殺之前&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;她一定會殺了夜神局長吧&#x202c;</p>
